ChatApp-

YO!

A real-time chat application for messaging with friends. This web-based chat app enables seamless communication with an intuitive user interface.

🚀 Features

Real-time messaging

User authentication 

Responsive UI for mobile and desktop

Secure message transmission

Multiple chat rooms 

🛠️ Technologies Used

Frontend: HTML, CSS, JavaScript (React)

Backend: Node.js, Express.js 

Database: MongoDB 

WebSockets: Socket.io 


📌 Installation

1️⃣ Clone the Repository

git clone https://github.com/Sahil-957/ChatApp.git  
cd ChatApp

2️⃣ Install Dependencies

npm install

3️⃣ Run the Project

npm start

🤝 Contribution

Feel free to contribute! Fork the repo, create a branch, and submit a pull request.


